        "source_page": 2,
        "source_text": "Typical performance of 3M Acrylic Foam Tape Series GT7100 is shown below. Peel and shear values depend on substrate characteristics and/or paint composition. These values are for reference only, and not to be used for specification purposes. For specification values please see the certificate of analysis.",
