        "source_page": 3,
        "source_text": "Shelf Life Three years from date of manufacture when stored at recommended storage condition 23°C +/-2°C and 50% +/-4% relative humidity. ... should be stored in typical storage conditions for pressure-sensitive adhesives used within the automotive industry.",
